padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-image: none;\"><strong>SUMMARY：</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-variant: normal; white-space: normal; float: none; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-style: normal; line-height: 28px;\">电影不只有讲述故事的用途，还能用来记录生活，感受生活，《童年》这部影片为我们展现了生活的琐碎、生命的精彩，生命的每一段旅程都是珍贵的财富，把握好幸福吧，因为逝去的时光无法倒带。</span></span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2. Boyhood<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn what might have been a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/gimmick\" target=\"_blank\">gimmick</a> but was really a stroke of genius, Richard Linklater began shooting Boyhood when its leading actor, Ellar Coltrane, was a first-grader and each succeeding summer shot a new <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/segment\" target=\"_blank\">segment</a> involving Coltrane's Mason and his Texas family: mother Olivia (Patricia Arquette), father Mason Sr. (Ethan Hawke) and elder sister Samantha (the director's daughter Lorelei). Mason's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/evolving\" target=\"_blank\">evolving</a> life has its difficulties but few extremities; it unfolds rather than exploding in reality-TV's manufactured <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/trauma\" target=\"_blank\">trauma</a>s. A home movie of a fictional home life, an epic assembled from <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/vignette\" target=\"_blank\">vignette</a>s, Boyhood <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shimmer\" target=\"_blank\">shimmer</a>s with unforced reality. To watch it is to page through a family album of folks you just met, yet feel you've known forever. This is life as most of us experience it, and which few movies document with such understated <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/acuity\" target=\"_blank\">acuity</a>. Embrace each moment, Linklater tells us, because it won't come again &mdash; unless he is there to record it, shape it and turn it into an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/indelible\" target=\"_blank\">indelible</a> movie.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<strong><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\">【英闻天天译】</a></strong>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2566/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">2.童年<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这也许会被认为是玩花样，但它确实是一部天才之作，理查德&middot;林柯莱特拍摄《童年》时，该片主演艾拉&middot;柯川正在上一年级，而接下来的每一个暑假都将拍摄一部新片，讲述柯川所饰演的主人公梅森梅森和他在德克萨斯的一家：母亲奥利维亚（帕特里夏&middot;阿奎特饰）、父亲梅森（伊桑&middot;霍克饰）和姐姐萨曼莎（罗蕾莱&mdash;&mdash;导演的女儿饰）。梅森的成长历程时有挫折但极少被逼至窘境；情节展开并不似真人秀那样加入大量的痛苦创伤。这是一部讲述家庭琐碎的电影，一部由短小片段组成的叙事片，《童年》这部影片处处闪现着毫不做作的现实。观看这部影片就好像在一页页翻阅你曾遇见过的人的家庭影集，每个感觉都似曾相识。这就是我们大多数人都经历过的生活，而极少有电影能做到如此敏锐的细节捕捉。林柯莱特通过这部影片告诉我们：珍惜每一个美好瞬间吧，逝去的时光无法倒流，除非有一个他在这里记录并将其定格为电影中的永恒瞬间。</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,0,0);\">2.《童年》<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这可能是个噱头，但真的是一次天才之举，理查德&bull;林克莱特开拍《童年》时，主演艾拉&bull;柯川正在读一年级，接下来每年夏天拍摄一集新片，包括柯川的梅森以及他在德克萨斯的家：母亲奥利维娅（帕特里夏&bull;阿奎特饰）、父亲梅森（伊桑&bull;霍克饰）以及姐姐萨曼莎（导演的女儿罗蕾莱饰）。梅森的生活遇到了困难，但还不至于到窘迫的地步；故事展开并非如真人秀电视所炮制的那种痛苦经历。《童年》是一部关于琐碎家庭事务的电影，像一集由拍摄花絮集结而成的电视片，闪烁着那种毫不做作的现实。看这部片子，就像一页页翻过你所遇之人的家庭相册，但感觉你早已知晓。这就是生活，我们大多数人所经历的，而很少有电影能有这样的敏锐度。林克莱特告诉我们，拥抱每一个瞬间，因为它不会再来了，除非有他在这里记录、塑造并制作成一部永不磨灭的电影。</span></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\