  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tStain<br />\n\tA stain is a mark left behind. What object was being staining? Was it an accident or was it done on purpose? What color was the stain?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: The stain stood out on the white background... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) staining the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/gel\" target=\"_blank\">gel</a> after the gel <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/electrophoresis\" target=\"_blank\">electrophoresis</a> process in DNA profiling<br />\n\t2) colorful tie dye t-shirts<br />\n\t3) hair highlight<br />\n\t4) food stain on a shirt just before an interview<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below. What will happen next?</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tOn his normally expressionless face, his eyes widened a bit when he recognized both the company name as well as the name of the key card owner. The company was where his partner was working as a &ldquo;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/janitor\" target=\"_blank\">janitor</a>,&rdquo; and the name was on the piece of paper his partner gave him. How interesting... he thought as he got closer to the seated man who was busy going through his pages in the hopes of the pages not being stained by the spilled liquid. Al stood behind him, but the man did not realize his presence nor his scanning of the document as he <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/shuffle\" target=\"_blank\">shuffle</a>d through the pages.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/161690545634/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718979/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p718979\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p710386/\">比尔盖茨推荐2014年5本必读好书</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720267/\">50岁老人希望自己在25岁做的事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p431046/\">告别单身从朋友下手 7招将朋友变成恋人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p720860/\">2014年英语四级多少分算过啊？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p481921/\">双语求职者优势大：7大工作机会在等你！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p558553/\">面试三句话必胜法则：马上有工作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p555885/\">只需五步！教你拍出超赞照片</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p703848/\">男人更臭美 比女人花更多时间美容</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p704614/\">幽默角度拍出创意旅行照</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
